    "title": "Awesome-LLM-for-Autonomous-Driving-Resources",
    "description": "A curated list of awesome LLM/VLM/VLA/World Model for Autonomous Driving(LLM4AD) resources (continually updated)",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "dateCreated": "2026-03-22T05:37:06.966Z",
